msgstr "ດີມອນ Wi-Fi AP ແບບສອງຊ່ອງສັນຍານ"

#: applications/luci-app-dcwapd/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/dcwapd/dcwapd.js:27
#: applications/luci-app-dcwapd/root/usr/share/luci/menu.d/luci-app-dcwapd.json:3
